Hello,

I am presenting you my lastest map ,his name is cs_ china_v2.(because it is the second version of the map)
It is an hostage map, which takes place in an asiatic village
This map is a bit small, though it is a real labyrinth, there is a net of undergrounds, which cross all the map.
I particularly worked on the game play, meshs, and lights.
